              <div class="mb-4">
                <strong>Tokyo Adventure - Day 1:</strong>
              </div>

              <div class="mb-4">
                <span>Tomorrow I'll visit </span>
                <span data-place="tokyo-tower" class="transition-colors duration-300">
                  <strong>Tokyo Tower</strong>, the iconic landmark offering stunning city views
                </span>
                <span>, then head to </span>
                <span data-place="sukiyabashi-jiro" class="transition-colors duration-300">
                  <strong>Sukiyabashi Jiro</strong> for the best sushi experience of my life
                </span>
                <span>. In the afternoon, I'll explore </span>
                <span data-place="shibuya-crossing" class="transition-colors duration-300">
                  <strong>Shibuya Crossing</strong>, the world's busiest intersection
                </span>
                <span>, and end the day relaxing at </span>
                <span data-place="hamarikyu-garden" class="transition-colors duration-300">
                  <strong>Hamarikyu Garden</strong>, a peaceful oasis in the heart of the city
